Class ControlPanel

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.awt.Component

  • All Implemented Interfaces:

    public class ControlPanel
extends javax.swing.JPanel
implements NumericalControlListener
    The Control panel manages all the numeric inputs for the color channels. It also hosts the Ok and Cancel buttons.
